# Cosign Container Signing — Status

> Status: ✅ COMPLETE
> Date: 2026-05-28
> Version: 0.1.0

---

## Deliverables

### 1. Cosign Setup ✅

| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `.github/workflows/sign-images.yml` | GitHub Actions workflow for keyless signing |
| `scripts/sign-image.sh` | Manual signing script (keyless) |
| `scripts/verify-image.sh` | Verification script with attestation support |

**Workflow jobs:**
- `build-sign-sbom` — Build multi-platform image
- `cosign-sign` — Keyless sign with Fulcio + Rekor
- `sbom-generation` — Syft SPDX SBOM generation + signing
- `slsa-provenance` — SLSA provenance attestation
- `github-attestation` — GitHub Actions attestation
- `verify-deployment-ready` — Pre-deployment verification gate

### 2. SBOM Generation ✅

| File | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `scripts/generate-sbom.sh` | Syft-based SBOM generation script |
| `.github/workflows/sign-images.yml` | SBOM upload to release artifacts |

**Features:**
- SPDX JSON format (default)
- CycloneDX support (optional)
- Automatic validation
- Cosign signature for SBOM artifacts
- Release artifact upload (on tags)

### 3. Attestation ✅

| Type | Implementation |
|------|----------------|
| SLSA Provenance | `slsa-github-generator` container workflow |
| GitHub Attestation | `actions/attest-build-provenance@v1` |
| Cosign Attestation | `cosign verify-attestation` support |

